This is the configuration and source for http://twistedmatrix.com/~diffresource.twistd/.

It is adminstered using braid[1]. It is installed in `/srv/diffresource` as user diffresource.
It uses the following directories

~/config - This repository.
~/bin - commands to start and stop the server
~/log - log files
~/run - pid files
~/divmod - A checkout of divmod (for combinator)
~/Projects - combinators working directory

The following fabric commands are available:

install - Create user and install configuration.
update - Updates the configuration and restarts the server.
start - Start server.
stop - Stop server.
restart - Restart the server.

[1] https://github.com/twisted-infra/braid
